text: Orsai is a Paraguayan comedy film directed and written by Emiliano Gómez. It was released on August 15, 2019 by Filmagic Entertainment. The film stars Rafael Alfaro and Paola Maltese, with Mexican actor Édgar Vivar, and Paraguayan former footballers Ever Hugo Almeida and Carlos Alberto Gamarra as special guest stars. == References == == External links == * Category:2019 films Category:2019 comedy films Category:Films shot in Paraguay Category:Paraguayan films
